[b]OK, If you people INSIST on leeching, at least give me and Mod Allstar SOME credit. But if people don't i'll take down the Download link.[/b]
[size=20pt]V2 IN MAKING!!!![/size]
OK, this is my first server release. I got 11 pictures to go along with it, plus my 2 email addresses, and some extras.
OK, I'm going to start off giving credits. %40 Mod Allstar for base and I left some places he made %60 Me, for the new areas+release!
There. I did not leech and to prove this is a clean, look at this virus scan picture:
[IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/z3a55.jpg[/img]
OK? Now you know it's not a key logger or virus or Trojan etc.
This server is Allstarscape V2 based...I took out the glitch with Mod Allstar logging in and ip banning everybody (Skillerzmine and fatality and rawr as well.) I used my custom compiler, I used to go by the name of Funny Man, so you will see that name pop up on like the compiler and above the log out button.
